description: Dinamico is a template pack for N2 CMS that uses MVC4/Razor. This is immediately usable templates built upon the N2 CMS framework. N2 CMS is a lightweight CMS library that can be used as is, or in combination with many features out of the box using template pack for MVC2, MVC3/razor or WebForms.
title: Dinamico Templates for N2 CMS
